displacementae.homomorphism.hpconfigs.hpsearch_config_block_lookup module¶

Hyperparameter-search configuration for Dsprites and Block MLP group representation¶

A configuration file for our custom hyperparameter search script. This configuration is meant for hyperparameter searches of the simulation defined by homomorphism.train_block_mlp_repr.
